					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think the same, that something's wrong with the power supply.
<br />The whole circuitry draws 180mA  @ 5V, which makes the 7805 (with large radiator) very hot after a few minutes. Also, there is a significant voltage drop in the top part of breadboard, if the power supply is connected on the bottom of it and viceversa.</div>

